| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5677 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e493d4a4-b232-5062-9f67-bf6fdacbfc16"
